<li><a href="/wiki/Adrian_Goldsworthy" title="Adrian Goldsworthy">Goldsworthy, Adrian</a>: <i>In the Name of Rome: The Men Who Won the Roman Empire</i> (Orion,2003) <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0753817896" class="internal">ISBN 0-7538-1789-6</a></li>
<li>Goldsworthy, A. (1997) "The Othismos, Myths and Heresies: The Nature of Hoplite Battle", <i>War In History</i> 4/1, pp.1-26</li>
<li>Hanson, V. (1989) "The Western Way of War" (Hodder &amp; Stoughton)</li>
<li>Lazenby, J.F. "The Pelopennesian War - A Military Study", (2004) Routledge</li>
